class_description:
An event emitted by a Preferences node to indicate that
 a child of that node has been added or removed. Note, that although NodeChangeEvent inherits Serializable interface from
 java.util.EventObject, it is not intended to be Serializable. Appropriate
 serialization methods are implemented to throw NotSerializableException.

params.param_description: The parent of the node that was added or removed.
The node that was added or removed.

return_description: The node that was added or removed.

Methods.method_description: Returns the node that was added or removed.

return_description: The parent Preferences node whose child was added or removed

Methods.method_description: Returns the parent of the node that was added or removed.
